---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Golfové ihrisko"
description: "9-jamkové ihriská GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK v Ivanke pri Nitre. Driving range, putting green, chipping area."
permalink: /golfove-ihrisko/
---
<section class="hero hero--inner">
  <div class="hero__bg"></div>
  <div class="hero__content">
    <p class="hero__eyebrow">Ivanka pri Nitre</p>
    <h1 class="hero__title">Golfové ihrisko</h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">Green Meadows &amp; Green Park</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="notice">
      <strong>2026:</strong> Ihriská GREEN MEADOWS a GREEN PARK sa striedajú — sledujte značenie pri vstupe do areálu.
    </div>

    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="section-label">Dve ihriská</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Vyberte si ihrisko</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Obe 9-jamkové ihriská ponúkajú jedinečný zážitok — Green Meadows s výhľadom na lúky, Green Park s prírodným rázom.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="courses-grid">
      {% for course in collections.courses %}
      <a href="/golfove-ihrisko/{{ course.data.slug }}/" class="course-card">
        <div class="course-card__img-wrap">
          <img src="{{ course.data.hero_image }}" alt="{{ course.data.title }}" class="course-card__img" loading="lazy">
          <div class="course-card__overlay">
            <div class="course-card__tag">9-jamkové ihrisko</div>
            <div class="course-card__name">{{ course.data.title }}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="course-card__body">
          <ul class="course-card__features">
            {% for f in course.data.features | limit(5) %}
            <li>{{ f }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          <div class="course-card__cta">Detail ihriska →</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--green">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="section-label">Areál</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Čo nájdete v areáli</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="quicklinks-grid">
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🏌</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Driving range 250 m</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Reálne fervejové odpalisko aj podložky pre dlhú hru</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">⛳</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Patovací green</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Dva druhy tráv — precvičte si patingovú techniku</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🎯</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Chipping area 2×</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Tri čipovacie gríny pre krátku hru a bunkerovú techniku</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🍽</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Terasa &amp; ketering</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Firemné akcie a turnaje, ketering od bagety až po *****</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">🏢</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Team building</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc">Firemné podujatia od 20,- EUR/osoba</div>
      </div>
      <div class="quicklink">
        <span class="quicklink__icon">📱</span>
        <div class="quicklink__title">Samoobsluha &amp; QR</div>
        <div class="quicklink__desc"><a href="/golfove-ihrisko/samoobsluha/">Platba green fee QR kódom</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
